itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Jarred Taylor finally get "Kurt From Australia" aka Vincent Marcus back on the show to talk about one of the most infamous episodes of all time, #nuketheroos.  After two long years, we finally get answers.  Vincent also drops some of his best impressions, including a breakdown voice by voice of Eminem's career. Great episode.
